name: Kinley Clark - Lez Be Honest Podcast

episodes.title: Isabella Flores: Public Breakup, Escaping a Religious Cult and Having a Cosmic Connection to the Sea
episodes.description: In this episode, we have Isabella Flores joining us! She's well-known here in Austin, TX, especially after her very public breakup with the Raw Dog Run Club Owner. Isabella opens up about the reasons behind their split, the challenges they faced, and how she managed to navigate such a public breakup. We also explore her passion for traveling, trying new experiences, and, believe it or not, escaping a religious cult. Yes, you heard that right! This is one of the most fascinating episodes I've ever done. Isabella's life story is so compelling that she should definitely consider writing a book about it. Tune in. Trust me, just trust me, you don’t wanna miss this one!
